基本概念
1.Concept
PaaS is an internal application platform built on Docker and Kubernetes.
You can think of it as a cloud mainframe, you can deploy a lot of applications on it, it will distribute necessary resources to each application.

2.Trust PaaS certificate
Download the certificate and trust it regarding your OS and browser settings, before using any services in PaaS. 
This removes warnings of browser and command line tools when using PaaS services.

3.Create PaaS account
Go to PaaS Portal and register your account using your corporate mail address. 